Hey MaryGirl, can't wait to see your other vids. Glad you're feeling better and I hope you get that camera you want. ❤ Till next time✌

I'd love to see a season where we have either a mad scientist (an immortal or vampire even so we could do it from the distant past to the present?) or aliens trying to manipulate human DNA (with monstrous results) and have it crossover with Asylum and Freak Show.  :)
